command \f[CR]SELECT DATABASE()\f[R] or retrieve the value via
\f[B]mariadb_get_infov(3)\f[R] API function.
.IP \[bu] 2
The default database can also be set by the db parameter in
\f[B]mysql_real_connect(3)\f[R].
